Package com.aston.group.stationdefender.utils.resources

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Inventory
    Inventory is a storage place for items that the player can use.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ItemFactory
    This class is responsible for handling what Items are created
    PlayerInventory
    PlayerInventory class is responsible for holding items in the Players' Inventory
    QuickSlot
    QuickSlot class allows the player inventory to have a limited number of items and each item takes up a slot.
    StackableInventory
    StackableInventory is an Inventory that allows Items to be stacked to allow more than one of the same type of item per slot
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Items
    This enum is responsible for holding a list of Items that can be created within the Game.
